deprec-core changelog
=====================

= 3.1.12  (Jul 30, 2011)

  * added pretty colors to terminal output
  * bugfix: use #{sudo} when setting owner

= 3.1.9  (Jul 28, 2011)

  * Moved rubygem deps from deprec to deprec-core
  * Added Rake as a Gem dependency

= 3.1.7  (Jul 22, 2011)

  * Added TEMPLATE_LOAD_PATH
    
    deprec-core will search this path for the template it's asked
    to render.
    
  * Did some reorganization of files.

= 3.1.5  (Jul 17, 2011)

  * Extracted the guts of deprec into this gem

